      <section eId="sec_2504_A">
        <num>2504-A</num>
        <heading>Hepatitis B immunization of a minor</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2504_A__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the term "health care practitioner" shall mean a person licensed,\ncertified or otherwise authorized to practice under title eight of the\neducation law, acting within his or her lawful scope of practice; and\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2504_A__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the term "capacity to consent" shall mean an individual's ability,\ndetermined without regard to the individual's age, to understand and\nappreciate the nature and consequences of the proposed immunization, and\nto make an informed decision concerning the immunization.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
